  "title": "Maintenance Technician / Facilities Technician #78387",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Wholesaler - Seafood</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Maintenance Technician / Facilities Technician</strong></li><li>Working Location: Jurong</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days (Mon - Fri: 7.30am - 4.30pm, Sat: 7.30am - 11.30am)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Up to $3200 + OT + AWS + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Carry out scheduled preventive maintenance for facilities (such as aircon servicing, electrical inspections, minor repairs on trucks/forklifts, pest control, etc.).</li><li>Perform routine daily maintenance tasks for the facilities.</li><li>Conduct basic troubleshooting for mechanical and electrical (M&E) systems.</li><li>Assist with minor M&E installations.</li><li>Coordinate and communicate with external contractors, technicians, and engineers as needed.</li><li>Undertake any other tasks or duties assigned by management.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Higher Nitec (ITC) or Nitec (NTC 2/NTC 3) in any engineering-related discipline, preferably Mechanical or Electrical Engineering.</li><li>At least 2 years of relevant work experience in facilities, building maintenance, or the mechanical/electrical field.</li><li>Experience with ammonia handling will be an added advantage.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#78387 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
